。消息透露，<span style=\"color: orange;\">草案列明分裂國家及顛覆國家政權罪行最高可被判終身監禁</span>，而在三個特定情況下中央保留管轄權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395997&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395997%26refer%3DShare&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=008fd4fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395997%26refer%3DShare&h=16f687a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395997&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會明天起一連三日召開會議，全國人大常委譚耀宗及有份列席的港區人大代表今日啟程前往北京。譚耀宗認為，目前討論反對意見，已經沒有意義，但會反映有關完善立法的意見，包括確保新聞自由，以及設立追溯期及<span style=\"color: orange;\">加重罰則的意見</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534432-20200627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534432-20200627.htm&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=a1c13144\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534432-20200627.htm&h=d7c1de94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534432-20200627.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwlXPiafyjLc&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=ac601233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881e4cb669f1a